OL,3,CMcVities factories get cash for
OL,4,Coverhaul
OL,6,FThe factory home to the Jaffa Cake and
OL,7,FChocolate Digestive will receive
OL,8,Finvestment and job opportunities in a
OL,9,Fbid to "supercharge" its growth.
OL,11,FThe parent company of McVitie's,
OL,12,FPladis, has announced a #68 million
OL,13,Finvestment into its brands, with "the
OL,14,Fbulk of the cash" earmarked for the
OL,15,FNorth West.
