OL,3,CMcVities factories get cash for
OL,4,Coverhaul
OL,6,FThe snack giant has said funds will be
OL,7,Fused to boost productivity across its
OL,8,Ffactories, with locations in the North
OL,9,FWest that produce Penguin bars, Jaffa
OL,10,FCakes, and Chocolate Digestives seeing
OL,11,Fmost of the investment.
OL,13,FA total of #33 million will be used to
OL,14,Foverhaul its Liverpool Aintree site,
OL,15,Fwhere Jacob's Crackers are baked -
OL,16,Fwhich had seen 361 jobs at risk of
OL,17,Fredundancy in 2023.
OL,19,FThe money will go towards the
OL,20,Finstallation of new ovens and
OL,21,Finfrastructure.
