OL,3,CMcVities factories get cash for
OL,4,Coverhaul
OL,6,FThe McVitie's factory in Stockport
OL,7,Fwill also see a #21 million
OL,8,Finvestment, including the introduction
OL,9,Fof a new chocolate moulding line,
OL,10,Fcreating 45 new jobs.
OL,12,FThe factory produces Jaffa Cakes and
OL,13,FPenguin bars, and the new equipment
OL,14,Fcould make 1,500 bars per minute.
OL,16,FMcVitie's Stockport factory is also
OL,17,Fhome to the chocolate refinery that
OL,18,Fproduces all the chocolate used to top
OL,19,Fdigestive biscuits, with an estimated
OL,20,F1.7 billion Chocolate Digestives sold
OL,21,Feach year.
