OL,6,FAnthony Coulson, general manager of
OL,7,Fthe Pladis Stockport factory, said:
OL,8,F"Our Stockport site has a proud
OL,9,Fhistory and an exciting future. 80
OL,10,Fmillion packets of McVitie's Chocolate
OL,11,FDigestives are made every year, with
OL,12,Fall of the chocolate made in Greater
OL,13,FManchester."
OL,15,FA hundred years of the chocolate
OL,16,Fdigestive: a success story made in
OL,17,FStockport
