OL,6,FMete Buyurgan, Pladis' UK and Ireland
OL,7,Fmanaging director, said: "We have a
OL,8,Ffantastic suite of much-loved brands,
OL,9,Fbaked by dedicated colleagues, and we
OL,10,Fhave a responsibility to continue to
OL,11,Fnurture these brands for customers and
OL,12,Fconsumers across the world."
OL,14,FRecent data revealed Pladis' snack
OL,15,Foperations generate almost #240
OL,16,Fmillion for the North West economy
OL,17,Feach year.
